    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cardinal Descent是一款卡牌构筑类Roguelike游戏，你可以制作元素协同效应并发现破坏游戏平衡的贴纸连击。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握元素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略性地使用基于元素的卡牌来执行你选择的连击。以正确的顺序出牌以最大化伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/f664fc72067a323612c2c6fc1778ce2a.poster.avif?t=1758590680\" width=630 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/f664fc72067a323612c2c6fc1778ce2a.webm?t=1758590680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/f664fc72067a323612c2c6fc1778ce2a.mp4?t=1758590680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >改变游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你的进展，你会解锁改变游戏的贴纸，这些贴纸会放置在你的卡牌上，在进展过程中发现酷炫的协同效应和连击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/25c187402b4213c7d96c1fc906b00a1b.poster.avif?t=1758590680\" width=630 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/25c187402b4213c7d96c1fc906b00a1b.webm?t=1758590680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/25c187402b4213c7d96c1fc906b00a1b.mp4?t=1758590680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打破游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >贴纸编辑和商店允许你制作完美的协同效应来造成疯狂的伤害量。你会打破游戏吗？还是它会超越你？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/9d8ac37707589f19bc336cc25072a051.poster.avif?t=1758590680\" width=630 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/9d8ac37707589f19bc336cc25072a051.webm?t=1758590680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/9d8ac37707589f19bc336cc25072a051.mp4?t=1758590680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
